Uses of Interface
net.objectzoo.delegates.FunctionAsyncResult

  • Packages that use FunctionAsyncResult 
    Package Description
    net.objectzoo.delegates
    This package contains the delegates of the Events4J API.
    net.objectzoo.delegates.adapters
    This package contains support classes that can be used to wrap standard delegates to be asynchronous.
    net.objectzoo.delegates.impl
    This package contains support classes that can be used to implement AsyndAction or AsyncFunction delegates.

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AsyncFutureTask<R>
      This FutureTask subclass is used internally for the asynchronous invocation of actions and funcions and implements the interfaces FunctionAsyncResult and ActionAsyncResult so that it directly serves as return value for the asynchronous invocations and as parameter given to the callback methods.
